overview[/iurl] • [b]12.[/b] [anchor=INFO]Hellhound[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/16/07 [img]http://img518.imageshack.us/img518/1541/newhellhoundpw0.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]Hellhounds, edited the way of doggy style[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]13.[/b] [anchor=GS]GodSwords[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/16/07 [img]http://img110.imageshack.us/img110/2334/godswordsit7.png[/img][img]http://img265.imageshack.us/img265/4349/zammyanim2hg6.png[/img][img]http://img411.imageshack.us/img411/8316/zammyanim1ht7.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]Really the strongest swords you'll ever see.[/i] [b]Going to add one day:[/b] [i]it's [s]animations and[/s] emotes.[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]14.[/b] [anchor=ZT]Zamorakian Trident[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/20/07 [img]http://img514.imageshack.us/img514/1949/ztridentve4.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]Zamorakian trident, wich is afcourse an evil item[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]15.[/b] [anchor=DEF]Defenders[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/21/07 [img]http://img227.imageshack.us/img227/7661/defenderszl4.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]Defenders, the defending weapons + I couldn't leave it to not let my Dragon defender became reality :P[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]16.[/b] [anchor=FC]New Fire Cape[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/27/07 [img]http://img529.imageshack.us/img529/6725/firecapeequipedqx5.gif[/img][img]http://img231.imageshack.us/img231/231/fcitemzr2.png[/img][img]http://img231.imageshack.us/img231/323/fc23ee2.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]A cape of 1000 degrees wich would burn you if you wear. I'm kinda a Burned Meat so that's why I'm still live =P[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]17.[/b] [anchor=LUN]Lunar[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 09/29/07 [img]http://img443.imageshack.us/img443/1710/lunarsf4.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]Lunar, the armor of the moonclan. quite cool don'tcha think?[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b]18.[/b] [anchor=BAG]Bandos Gate[/anchor] [b]Date made:[/b] 10/10/07 [img]http://img521.imageshack.us/img521/141/bandosgatedq0.png[/img] [b]comment:[/b] [i]How the hell would you else expect Bandos to come in a dungeon =P?[/i] • [iurl=#top]Return to Cache Edits overview[/iurl] • [b][========================= [i][u]end of Cache Edits[/u][/i] =========================][/b] [anchor=Comment][/anchor] Love the Items, Npcs and OBject. I quit coding Private servers but however I'm not releasing this cache. my idea was to finish my runescape project private server (the last thing I would call a challange for Pservers) I ended with a 6/8 of getting as close to runescape. after I normally had a 'close-to-runescape' source I was planning on releasing this client so It would connect to my server. [b]Q:[/b] [i]So why don't you release the cache?[/i] [b]A:[/b] [i]My project was unfinished (aswell as most of my projects where unfinished) and they can already model mask the Items. Someone will sooner or later get the brain to figure out how to add NPCs, Objects, Emotes and Graphix.[/i] I now started coding C++. I actually thought about something that I was telling to others almost all the time
Why start a development team? why not just make a game on your own?
some friends and I are going to make a game on our own. It's better then just wait ti'll Jagex releases something so we could copy it. This could be my last message but who knows, I might return to Private servers someday. Goodbye.
